==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exactly
<hw>Ex*act"ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an exact manner; precisely
according to a rule, standard, or fact; accurately; strictly; correctly;
nicely.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Exactly</xex> wrought.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>His enemies were pleased, for he had acted <qex>exactly</qex> as
their interests required.</q> <rj><qau>Bancroft.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Exactness</ent>⟦br⟧
